<title>“这是法国的投降书”</title>
<link>http://weixin.sogou.com/weixin?type=2&amp;query=%E7%8E%AF%E7%90%83%E6%97%B6%E6%8A%A5+%E2%80%9C%E8%BF%99%E6%98%AF%E6%B3%95%E5%9B%BD%E7%9A%84%E6%8A%95%E9%99%8D%E4%B9%A6%E2%80%9D</link>
